Edit groups

Options:
  -h, --help             show this help message
      --compatibility-version  compatibility version to force
  -s, --script           suppress extraneous human friendly messages and use JSON output
  -a, --as               user to run commands as (default: akim)
      --path             file whose acl to group
  -n, --name             name of the acl to group
      --create         
      --delete         
      --show             list group users, administrators and description
      --description      acl description
      --add-user         add user to group (default: [])
      --add-group        add group to group (default: [])
      --add-admin        add administrator to group (default: [])
      --add              add users, administrators and groups to group (prefix: @<group>, ^<admin> (default: [])
      --remove-user      remove user from group (default: [])
      --remove-group     remove group from group (default: [])
      --remove-admin     remove administrator from group (default: [])
      --remove           remove users, administrators and groups from group (prefix: @<group>, ^<admin> (default: [])
  -v, --verbose          use verbose output
  -f, --fetch            fetch acl from https://beyond.infinit.sh
